{"tid":659564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"觀塘小巴撞過路婦 重創昏迷  現場並非行人過路處","createTime":"2018-05-10T02:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T03:56:53.000Z","uid":122,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6291a50a3db377ee33e15730a17c905252dc31cf","tid":659564,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T02:40:17.000Z","msg":"觀塘小巴撞過路婦 重創昏迷<br />\n<br />\n早上7時38分，觀塘協和街發生交通意外。一輛紅頂小巴沿協和街落斜，駛過同仁街交界後，撞倒一名由左至右步出過馬路的老婦。傷者姓石71歲，頭部重創當場昏迷，稍後由救護車送到伊利沙伯醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>現場並非行人過路處，小巴車尾方向約50米有紅綠燈</strong></span>，警方正調查車禍原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180510/58173879?_ga=2.194287150.2092810447.1525919822-1059663393.1525919822\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180510%2F58173879%3F_ga%3D2.194287150.2092810447.1525919822-1059663393.1525919822&d=3680jztEDHKTRDWNjPSfFTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=75ff6785\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180510%2F58173879%3F_ga%3D2.194287150.2092810447.1525919822-1059663393.1525919822&h=b0ef4836\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180510/58173879?_ga=2.194287150.2092810447.1525919822-1059663393.1525919822</a>"},{"pid":"c678b84edf25a8fec4e8a4ab8e45b6a0e476ac6a","tid":659564,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T03:54:34.000Z","msg":"老野又害人"},{"pid":"808ae1f7adeb99cfcc3df749f8e0250d783604f4","tid":659564,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T03:56:27.000Z","msg":"我賽跑冠軍黎架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742c8e37a61a2f460fa5112dc6e411845d8b5efa","tid":659564,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T03:56:53.000Z","msg":"想死就行遠D"}]}